### ⚠️ Turnaround Alert
The target turnaround for a **Mutual NDA is 2 business days** (Policy §5). The agreement is dated **April 18, 2026** — that window has elapsed as of today (April 22). Legal Ops should assess whether escalation to the **Legal Operations Lead** is required before proceeding.

